                "invention-title": [
                    "Preparation method of high-purity mercaptopurine",
                    "一种高纯度巯嘌呤的制备方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention relates to the technical field of medicine synthesis, and discloses a preparation method of high-purity mercaptopurine, which comprises the following steps: by taking hypoxanthine as a raw material and anisole as a reaction solvent, carrying out heating reflux synthesis in a container to obtain mercaptopurine, and ending the reaction when hypoxanthine disappears; filtering the reaction liquid under reduced pressure to obtain a filter cake A; recrystallizing the obtained filter cake A with water, and decolorizing with activated carbon to obtain a mercaptopurine crude product B; continuously dissolving the mercaptopurine crude product B in 300V boiling water, refining, and filtering to obtain a mercaptopurine semi-finished product C; adding the semi-finished product C into 20V boiling water, adding stronger ammonia water to help dissolving, and cooling to separate out a mercaptopurine finished product D; compared with the prior art, the method provided by the invention has the advantages of simple process, no generation of hydrogen sulfide gas, avoidance of air pollution, high product purity and low cost, and is suitable for industrial production."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明涉及医药合成技术领域，且公开了一种高纯度巯嘌呤的制备方法，包括以次黄嘌呤为原料，苯甲醚作为反应溶剂，在容器中加热回流合成得巯嘌呤，次黄嘌呤消失为反应终点；反应液减压过滤得到滤饼A；所得滤饼A用水重结晶并使有活性炭脱色制得巯嘌呤粗品B；将巯嘌呤粗品B继续溶于300V沸水中精制后过滤得到巯嘌呤半成品C；半成品C加入到20V沸水中，加入浓氨水助溶后降温析出得到巯嘌呤成品D。本发明方案与现有技术相比工艺简单，没有硫化氢气体的产生，避免了空气污染，产物纯度高，成本低廉，适于工业化生产。"
                }
            ]
